description: Excel is an extremely great tool for receiving information and meaning out of huge amounts of data. This course is about learning the most important basic features of Excel 2013. This course includes every tiny detail that you will need to know to master the basics of Excel 2013. So even if this is your first time using Excel 2013, by the end of this course you will have learned all the essential skills needed. The beauty of this course is that you don't have to sit for hours and hours to finish a course, you will finish this course within an hour at max. This course is structured in a way where it build on to a previous lecture. Therefore go in the order the course has been layout.
title: Improve Productivity & Performance with Basic Excel 2013
